01:13:07,862 --> 01:13:11,000
to listen and learn about
the Hawaiians' beliefs.

926
01:13:13,275 --> 01:13:18,793
Lanakila has agreed
to show Lucianne
how Mauna Kea is honored.

927
01:13:47,344 --> 01:13:50,517
The Hawaiians have
their own cosmology

928
01:13:50,551 --> 01:13:53,931
expressed in these
traditional songs and dances.

929
01:13:55,241 --> 01:13:58,931
Every little step
and gesture has
a significance

930
01:13:58,965 --> 01:14:01,482
connected with
the sacred volcano.

931
01:14:03,137 --> 01:14:06,620
Here on the mountain,
too much human footprints,
or walking,

