01:14:11,793 --> 01:14:13,413
From the snow, the ice,

935
01:14:13,448 --> 01:14:15,517
and how it needs
to percolate and move.

936
01:14:15,551 --> 01:14:18,379
So we have to allow
the forces of nature
to do its thing.

937
01:14:18,413 --> 01:14:22,586
So that very simple hula,
where you see us dancers

938
01:14:22,620 --> 01:14:24,689
retreating with
this very light tapping

