01:14:35,241 --> 01:14:36,482
Not even our footprints.

943
01:14:42,517 --> 01:14:46,137
Lanakila sees humans
as a part of creation

944
01:14:46,172 --> 01:14:48,586
and we ignore this
at our peril.

945
01:14:53,517 --> 01:14:55,172
When you break away
from that thinking

946
01:14:55,206 --> 01:14:57,206
or if you think
yourself outside, or worse,

