01:15:06,103 --> 01:15:08,655
This is after human impact.

951
01:15:08,689 --> 01:15:12,379
Has all the native forests
of this mountain be decimated.

952
01:15:21,137 --> 01:15:23,206
So what
do you think
when you hear people

953
01:15:23,241 --> 01:15:26,793
saying that, you know,
now that they have
used the Earth,

