01:15:28,862 --> 01:15:32,448
Say, planets around
other stars or Mars,
or wherever it happens to be?

956
01:15:33,103 --> 01:15:34,620
It's a scary thought for me

957
01:15:34,655 --> 01:15:37,379
to think of people
wanting to go
and their whole mission

958
01:15:37,413 --> 01:15:41,172
just to go and continue
the extraction process
on other planets.

959
01:15:42,034 --> 01:15:43,103
Absolutely not.

960
01:15:43,137 --> 01:15:46,827
You know, there's so much more
to learn right here.

961
01:15:46,862 --> 01:15:48,689
And so in many cases,
I think it's important

962
01:15:48,724 --> 01:15:51,137
that we need to protect
the rest of the universe
from us.

963
01:15:57,206 --> 01:16:02,551
Lucianne Walkowicz
has drawn conclusions
from this message.

964
01:16:06,068 --> 01:16:08,965
I think
the problem that I have
with colonization

965
01:16:09,000 --> 01:16:12,758
as described
