966
01:16:12,793 --> 01:16:16,379
is that it really
does describe colonization.

967
01:16:16,413 --> 01:16:18,551
The idea of going places

968
01:16:18,586 --> 01:16:20,586
and extracting and exploiting.

969
01:16:20,620 --> 01:16:23,482
The same kind of colonization
projected into space

970
01:16:23,517 --> 01:16:26,517
that many people
have experienced
here on Earth.

