01:16:26,551 --> 01:16:29,379
Now on Earth, we do face
existential threats.

972
01:16:29,413 --> 01:16:31,724
We do have things
like climate change

973
01:16:31,758 --> 01:16:35,413
that are creating
a less habitable world
than the one

974
01:16:35,448 --> 01:16:37,206
that has raised
our species thus far.

975
01:16:37,241 --> 01:16:40,379
And we can't afford
to treat our planet

976
01:16:40,413 --> 01:16:42,137
