soul-drenching,

980
01:16:59,344 --> 01:17:02,896
life-supporting richness
and lushness

981
01:17:02,931 --> 01:17:06,413
that exists on
no other planet
that we know of.

982
01:17:06,448 --> 01:17:09,862
And that even if
we were to find a planet
around another star

983
01:17:09,896 --> 01:17:13,172
that we think,
might potentially
be like this,

984
01:17:13,206 --> 01:17:14,586
we would have
no way of knowing,

985
01:17:14,620 --> 01:17:19,448
