human beings reaching there
in our lifetimes.

986
01:17:19,482 --> 01:17:22,862
And yet here we are
surrounded by a paradise.

987
01:17:29,275 --> 01:17:32,758
I just feel so humbled by
the planet that we live on.

988
01:17:32,793 --> 01:17:36,793
Especially as someone
who thinks often
of other worlds.

989
01:17:36,827 --> 01:17:39,379
That I can swim in the ocean.

990
01:17:39,413 --> 01:17:42,103
That I can drink from streams.

991
01:17:42,137 --> 01:17:44,793
That I can sit out and feel
the sun on my face.

992
01:17:44,827 --> 01:17:47,482
And I know that it
doesn't just not harm me,

